  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">We report on the recent results revealing the presence of geometric invariants in all the phenomena in which vacuum condensates appear and we show that Aharonov--Anandan phase can be used to provide the evidence of phenomena like Hawking and Unruh effects and to test some behavior of quantum field theory in curved space. A very precise quantum thermometer can be also built by using geometric invariants.</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
  </datafield>
